p.strong: If Toggle Fails (Reading RAX on Entry):

div.p: On Entry Stop, regs.rax still contains the result of the PREVIOUS syscall.
Result: Tracer reports incorrect return values and misattributes errors.

g.text: 0x80 | unsigned long long | orig_rax | SYSCALL NR
0x80 | unsigned long long | orig_rax | SAME SYSCALL NR
0x50 | unsigned long long | rax | RETURN VALUE
Stale Value if read at Entry
